      "content": "The Disney Characters API provides REST and GraphQL interfaces to a comprehensive database of Disney characters across films, TV shows, video games, and park attractions. The API covers 9,820+ Disney characters from all Disney brands including Walt Disney Animation, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars, and National Geographic. No authentication is required for read access.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Disney API",
